18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_21eb497b66eb1a1a','What is your name?','Sean Lin',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(166,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_6ca3809bc801ea0c','What gender do you identify with?','Male',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(167,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_cca57fe036393e59','What is your age range?','31 - 40',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(168,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_7bc5e7f6b5915a1e','Where are you from?','Taiwan',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(169,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_43daedac0a08cf8c','What OS are you using?','MacOS',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(170,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_fb99225770e4860f','Have you ever used a mechanical keyboard before?','No',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(171,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_912b7c9823702d30','How would you rate this product on a scale of 1 - 5?','4',4.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(172,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_4f186aae6dfa147f','Briefly, can you tell us why you\'ve rated it this way.','The keyboard excels in several areas, earning a perfect 5/5 for its design, typing experience, typing sound, and stable connection. However, the one area of concern is battery life, which lowers the overall rating.  I fully charged the keyboard to 80-90% on August 13, but by August 22, I received a \"low battery\" notification indicating it was at 25%. After charging it to 100% on August 22, the battery had dropped to 65% by August 28. Based on this usage pattern, it seems the keyboard may require charging approximately twice a month, which is more frequent than I had anticipated.',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(173,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_a9b70e9268acdf03','Overall how would you rate the software experience?','5',5.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(174,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_44297eef83590efd','Can you share more?','The software experience is exceptional. Upon connecting it to my MacBook, the keyboard is seamlessly recognized in both the Options+ and Tune. These apps provide a clear, detailed visual representation of the keyboard and offer a smooth, intuitive experience when navigating and interacting with their features.',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(175,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_939652c6f1af35de','How easy to follow was the onboarding for Fujian? (1 = Very difficult)','5',5.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(176,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_654f809d7dae0168','Did you customize the Action keys?','Yes',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(177,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_4b4d5ae4d5ffb626','Can you tell us more?','Changing the brightness on this keyboard is easy and intuitive. When I press F4, a pop-up window appears, making it simple to see and select the desired brightness level.\n\nOne suggestion for improvement would be to include an ambient light sensor, similar to the MacBook keyboard\'s ability to automatically adjust brightness based on surrounding light conditions. On my MacBook keyboard, I rarely have to manually change brightness (and I just realized there’s no dedicated brightness key on it!).',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(178,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_008c7d2b7f3a3d77','How would your rate the overall typing experience with this keyboard?','5',5.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(179,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_866037fcddacafe6','How do you feel about the sound while typing?','5',5.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(180,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_0f078b1d055e3736','Please tell us more','ompared to my previous keyboard, the MX Keys S, the new keyboard appears to require more frequent charging. However, charging it is hassle-free and convenient, as the keyboard uses a USB Type-C cable, which is widely available.',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(181,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_57c116fc87b3693b','This keyboard feels sturdy','4',4.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(182,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_fe53237382c01c82','How did you feel about the keyboard legs? (1= Very poor)','5',5.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(183,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_abcf1cc199f381e3','How secure did the USB dongle feel in the USB storage space on the back of the keyboard? (1 = Not very secure)','5',5.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(184,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_0f078b1d055e3736','Please tell us more','ompared to my previous keyboard, the MX Keys S, the new keyboard appears to require more frequent charging. However, charging it is hassle-free and convenient, as the keyboard uses a USB Type-C cable, which is widely available.',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(185,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_ad77dfaf113ba7a8','How satisfied are you with the battery life of the keyboard ?','2',2.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(186,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_08a83026b7b0749d','How satisfied are you with the charging of the keyboard ?','4',4.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(187,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_0f078b1d055e3736','Please tell us more','ompared to my previous keyboard, the MX Keys S, the new keyboard appears to require more frequent charging. However, charging it is hassle-free and convenient, as the keyboard uses a USB Type-C cable, which is widely available.',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(188,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_3818fe0ae092f1b6','How would you rate the backlit keys overall?','4',4.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(189,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_d0fd335936075623','How would you rate the brightness of the backlighting?','4',4.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(190,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_5d118267976b3797','Tell us more','I absolutely love the backlighting of this keyboard. Thanks to its crystal-like case, the backlighting not only illuminates the keycaps but also highlights most of the keyboard\'s components. I\'m using the graphite version, and the white lighting gives it a futuristic and cool aesthetic.\n\nOne detail worth noting is that the Bopomofo symbols are applied using stickers, which means they do not light up—this is a slight drawback compared to the MacBook keyboard.',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(191,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_6bb5008eb1542066','How often did you turn the backlit keys off?','I never turned the backlight off',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(192,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_0cec647b3dbe9ee3','What level (brightness) of backlighting did you choose?','My backlighting was at the mid-brightness setting',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(193,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_7fc40c8ecd98b168','How intuitive was it to change the backlight brightness? (1 = Very unintuitive)','5',5.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(194,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_4b4d5ae4d5ffb626','Can you tell us more?','Changing the brightness on this keyboard is easy and intuitive. When I press F4, a pop-up window appears, making it simple to see and select the desired brightness level.\n\nOne suggestion for improvement would be to include an ambient light sensor, similar to the MacBook keyboard\'s ability to automatically adjust brightness based on surrounding light conditions. On my MacBook keyboard, I rarely have to manually change brightness (and I just realized there’s no dedicated brightness key on it!).',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(195,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_32aa8dd2e7f94875','Can you rate the look of the keycaps?','4',4.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(196,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_a7b8b58f255317bf','Can you rate the feel of the keycaps?','5',5.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(197,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_e620d43d83722587','Can you elaborate?','While I’ve encountered two major challenges—keyboard weight and battery life—I believe both are manageable and do not detract significantly from its overall quality.\n\nThe keyboard is quite heavy, but considering it’s not a device you’d typically carry around, the weight is acceptable. Regarding battery life, needing to charge it twice a week initially felt frequent to me. However, after researching further, I found that this is normal for mechanical keyboards, especially with the backlighting turned on.\n\nWith these considerations in mind, I think this is a well-designed product that is ready for market release.',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(198,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_52564b4f93bb450d','I would recommend this product to a friend.','9',9.00,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(199,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_e620d43d83722587','Can you elaborate?','While I’ve encountered two major challenges—keyboard weight and battery life—I believe both are manageable and do not detract significantly from its overall quality.\n\nThe keyboard is quite heavy, but considering it’s not a device you’d typically carry around, the weight is acceptable. Regarding battery life, needing to charge it twice a week initially felt frequent to me. However, after researching further, I found that this is normal for mechanical keyboards, especially with the backlighting turned on.\n\nWith these considerations in mind, I think this is a well-designed product that is ready for market release.',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(200,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_8d9429894f670a3e','Taking into consideration any functional hurdles you\'ve come across with this device, do you believe it\'s ready for a market release?','Yes',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(201,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_e620d43d83722587','Can you elaborate?','While I’ve encountered two major challenges—keyboard weight and battery life—I believe both are manageable and do not detract significantly from its overall quality.\n\nThe keyboard is quite heavy, but considering it’s not a device you’d typically carry around, the weight is acceptable. Regarding battery life, needing to charge it twice a week initially felt frequent to me. However, after researching further, I found that this is normal for mechanical keyboards, especially with the backlighting turned on.\n\nWith these considerations in mind, I think this is a well-designed product that is ready for market release.',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(202,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_54fdfe83950615c9','Please let us know any other comments you have about your experience with this device.',NULL,NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(203,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_7144c9a9217c2254','What was your favorite thing about this product?','The typing sound is, without a doubt, my favorite feature. I haven’t used a mechanical keyboard since high school, and I’ve missed that familiar, satisfying sound. It transforms typing into a more vibrant and enjoyable experience. However, my wife occasionally complains about the noise whenever she walks by—though I can’t say I mind!',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(204,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_ec4274a61b6ab8d5','What\'s one thing that you think we can still improve on this product?','I would say the battery life—it would be ideal if it could last for at least a month before needing a recharge. I understand that the backlighting consumes significant energy, but incorporating a sensor to automatically adjust brightness based on ambient light could make the keyboard more eco-friendly and user-friendly.',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(205,12,6,'userid_fb8b4fd007e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_0d1e464662a6ec23','Do you agree to be contacted for follow up questions from the internal teams?','I agree, I\'m willing to help!',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:26:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00','2026-02-13 03:09:00'),(206,12,7,'userid_fb8b50e707e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_21eb497b66eb1a1a','What is your name?','Atom Wu',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:48:00','2026-02-13 03:09:03','2026-02-13 03:09:03'),(207,12,7,'userid_fb8b50e707e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_6ca3809bc801ea0c','What gender do you identify with?','Male',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:48:00','2026-02-13 03:09:03','2026-02-13 03:09:03'),(208,12,7,'userid_fb8b50e707e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_cca57fe036393e59','What is your age range?','31 - 40',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:48:00','2026-02-13 03:09:03','2026-02-13 03:09:03'),(209,12,7,'userid_fb8b50e707e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_7bc5e7f6b5915a1e','Where are you from?','Taiwan',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:48:00','2026-02-13 03:09:03','2026-02-13 03:09:03'),(210,12,7,'userid_fb8b50e707e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_43daedac0a08cf8c','What OS are you using?','Windows',NULL,'2025-08-29 15:48:00','2026-02-13 03:09:03','2026-02-13 03:09:03'),(211,12,7,'userid_fb8b50e707e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_fb99225770e4860f','Have you ever used a mechanical keyboard before?','Yes - I liked it',NU