:10','2026-02-13 03:10:10'),(1177,12,30,'userid_fb8b534207e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_7fc40c8ecd98b168','How intuitive was it to change the backlight brightness? (1 = Very unintuitive)','4',4.00,'2025-09-25 08:53:00','2026-02-13 03:10:10','2026-02-13 03:10:10'),(1178,12,30,'userid_fb8b534207e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_4b4d5ae4d5ffb626','Can you tell us more?',NULL,NULL,'2025-09-25 08:53:00','2026-02-13 03:10:10','2026-02-13 03:10:10'),(1179,12,30,'userid_fb8b534207e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_32aa8dd2e7f94875','Can you rate the look of the keycaps?','3',3.00,'2025-09-25 08:53:00','2026-02-13 03:10:10','2026-02-13 03:10:10'),(1180,12,30,'userid_fb8b534207e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_a7b8b58f255317bf','Can you rate the feel of the keycaps?','3',3.00,'2025-09-25 08:53:00','2026-02-13 03:10:10','2026-02-13 03:10:10'),(1181,12,30,'userid_fb8b534207e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_e620d43d83722587','Can you elaborate?','Regardless of my personal opinion, the fact that gasket keyboards are selling like hotcakes in the Chinese market makes me confident they\'ll appeal to gadget enthusiasts who love the latest and greatest.',NULL,'2025-09-25 08:53:00','2026-02-13 03:10:10','2026-02-13 03:10:10'),(1182,12,30,'userid_fb8b534207e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_52564b4f93bb450d','I would recommend this product to a friend.','5',5.00,'2025-09-25 08:53:00','2026-02-13 03:10:10','2026-02-13 03:10:10'),(1183,12,30,'userid_fb8b534207e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_e620d43d83722587','Can you elaborate?','Regardless of my personal opinion, the fact that gasket keyboards are selling like hotcakes in the Chinese market makes me confident they\'ll appeal to gadget enthusiasts who love the latest and greatest.',NULL,'2025-09-25 08:53:00','2026-02-13 03:10:10','2026-02-13 03:10:10'),(1184,12,30,'userid_fb8b534207e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_8d9429894f670a3e','Taking into consideration any functional hurdles you\'ve come across with this device, do you believe it\'s ready for a market release?','Yes',NULL,'2025-09-25 08:53:00','2026-02-13 03:10:10','2026-02-13 03:10:10'),(1185,12,30,'userid_fb8b534207e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_e620d43d83722587','Can you elaborate?','Regardless of my personal opinion, the fact that gasket keyboards are selling like hotcakes in the Chinese market makes me confident they\'ll appeal to gadget enthusiasts who love the latest and greatest.',NULL,'2025-09-25 08:53:00','2026-02-13 03:10:10','2026-02-13 03:10:10'),(1186,12,30,'userid_fb8b534207e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_54fdfe83950615c9','Please let us know any other comments you have about your experience with this device.',NULL,NULL,'2025-09-25 08:53:00','2026-02-13 03:10:10','2026-02-13 03:10:10'),(1187,12,30,'userid_fb8b534207e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_7144c9a9217c2254','What was your favorite thing about this product?','The distinctive tactile feedback of the gasket',NULL,'2025-09-25 08:53:00','2026-02-13 03:10:10','2026-02-13 03:10:10'),(1188,12,30,'userid_fb8b534207e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_ec4274a61b6ab8d5','What\'s one thing that you think we can still improve on this product?','Key size. Personally, I think if the keycap size could be adjusted to be about the size of the MX Mechanical Mini, combined with this typing feel, it would make for the ultimate product.',NULL,'2025-09-25 08:53:00','2026-02-13 03:10:10','2026-02-13 03:10:10'),(1189,12,30,'userid_fb8b534207e01','c18b9f2a-e2f5-477f-9',14,'UTSurveyType0006','Q_0d1e464662a6ec23','Do you agree to be contacted for follow up questions from the internal teams?','I  disagree, please don\'t contact me.',NULL,'2025-09-25 08:53:00','2026-02-13 03:10:10','2026-02-13 03:10:10');
